cases.question: Bottom 20 country by revenue for confirmed bookings
cases.ground_truth_sql:
SELECT TOP 20 AgentCountry,
       SUM(AgentSellingPrice) AS revenue
FROM BookingData
WHERE BookingStatus = 'Confirmed'
GROUP BY AgentCountry
ORDER BY revenue ASC
